headline: CME Group, IBD Stock Of The Day, Rides Market Volatility To Record High
summary: Market volatility is driving higher trading volumes for CME Group. CME stock received an upgrade Monday.

headline: Cboe Global Markets Plans to Launch S&P 500® Equal Weight Index Options on April 14, 2025
summary: Cboe Global Markets, Inc. (Cboe: CBOE), the world's leading derivatives and securities exchange network today announced plans to launch options on the S&P 500 Equal Weight Index (EWI) on April 14, 2025, pending regulatory review. The new initiative was announced today at the 50th International Futures Industry Conference in Boca Raton, Florida.
